sequenceDiagram
    participant MM as ModelMesh Serving
    participant KS as KServe<br/>(Knative Eventing)
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Storage as Storage Backend<br/>(PVC / DB / MinIO)
    participant Inference as KServe/ModelMesh<br/>Inference Service
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>(ServiceMonitor)
    participant Client as API Client

    Note over MM, Storage: Flow 1: ModelMesh Inference Payload Ingestion
    MM->>TrustyAI: POST /consumer/kserve/v2<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (cluster-internal)
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: ModelMeshInferencePayloadReconciler<br/>match request/response by inference ID
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Persist dataframe<br/>File I/O (PVC) / JDBC 3306 (DB) / HTTPS (MinIO)

    Note over KS, Storage: Flow 2: KServe CloudEvent Inference Ingestion
    KS->>TrustyAI: CloudEvent trigger<br/>org.kubeflow.serving.inference.request/response<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: KServeInferencePayloadReconciler<br/>match request/response by inference ID
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Persist dataframe<br/>File I/O / JDBC / HTTPS

    Note over TrustyAI, Prom: Flow 3: Scheduled Metric Computation & Prometheus Publication
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: PrometheusScheduler<br/>(cron: service.metrics-schedule, default 5s)
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Read inference data
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Dataframes
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: Compute fairness/drift metrics<br/>→ PrometheusPublisher (Micrometer gauges)
    Prom->>TrustyAI: GET /q/metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SA)
    TrustyAI-->>Prom: trustyai_* Prometheus gauges

    Note over Client, Inference: Flow 4: Explainability Request (disabled in RHOAI profile)
    Client->>TrustyAI: POST /explainers/local/lime<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (TLS optional on 4443)
    TrustyAI->>Inference: gRPC KServe v2 inference call<br/>cluster-internal, plaintext
    Inference-->>TrustyAI: Model prediction result
    TrustyAI-->>Client: Explanation response (JSON)

    Note over TrustyAI, Storage: Flow 5: PVC-to-Database Migration
    TrustyAI->>TrustyAI: HibernateDataSource @PostConstruct<br/>detect legacy PVC files at /inputs
    TrustyAI->>Storage: Read legacy CSV files (PVCStorage)
    Storage-->>TrustyAI: Legacy dataframes
    TrustyAI->>Storage: HibernateMigrator → MariaDB/MySQL<br/>JDBC 3306/TCP, username/password
